data.description: "Discover perfection at 11414 Switchgrass St in Kearney, MO. This 2022 custom-built home leaves no detail overlooked. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths, it offers spacious and modern living. The open-concept design invites you in, while the unfinished walkout basement holds endless possibilities for customization. Outside, a generous green space awaits in the backyard. Don't miss this opportunity to call this meticulously designed home your own!"
